  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting National and Regional Campaigns in LAC</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to support country and regional teams to devise, implement and evaluate regional and national campaigns. The support will be geared towards both the design phase through ad hoc support, exchanges and trainings to ensure campaigns develop a clear theory of change identifying key targets and audiences. During the implementation phase teams will be supported by ensuring the use of appropriate tools and techniques in terms of research, advocacy, media, communications, digital and social media.</narrative>
  </description>
